Description: Provides diagnostic tools for identifying influential cases and studies in multilevel meta-analysis (3-level models). Implements leave-one-out procedures for rma.mv objects, calculating DFBETAS, Cook's distance, and changes in variance components to assess the stability of pooled effect sizes.
